trans-unit.source: Provides a framework for <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Panel"></xref> elements that virtualize their child data collection.
trans-unit.target: Gir et rammeverk for <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Panel"> </xref> elementer som virtualisere datainnsamlingen underordnede.

trans-unit.source: This is an abstract class.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en abstrakt klasse.

trans-unit.source: In this context, "virtualize" refers to a technique by which a subset of [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] elements are generated from a larger number of data items based on which items are visible on the screen.
trans-unit.target: I denne konteksten "virtualisere" refererer til en metode som et delsett av [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] elementer som genereres fra flere dataelementer basert på hvilke elementer som vises på skjermen.

trans-unit.source: It is intensive, both in terms of memory and processor, to generate a large number of [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] elements when only a few may be on the screen at a given time.
trans-unit.target: Det er dataintensive både når det gjelder minne og prosessor til å generere et stort antall [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] elementer når bare noen få kan være på skjermen om gangen.

trans-unit.source: A panel that inherits from VirtualizingPanel, such as the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingStackPanel>, calculates visible items and works with the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator> from an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> (such as <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListView>) to only create [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] elements for visible items.
trans-unit.target: Et panel som arver fra VirtualizingPanel, som den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingStackPanel>beregner synlige elementer og fungerer med den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>fra en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>(eksempel <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox>eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListView>) til å opprette bare [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] synlige elementer som skal.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListView> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingStackPanel>

trans-unit.source: The following lists describes cases when the VirtualizingPanel cannot virtualize item containers: - The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> contains item containers of different types.
trans-unit.target: De følgende listene beskriver tilfeller når VirtualizingPanel ikke kan virtualisere elementet beholdere: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>inneholder elementet beholdere forskjellige typer.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: For example, a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Menu> might have items that use both <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Separator> objects as the item containers.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Menu>kan ha elementer som bruker både <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem>og <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Separator>objekter som elementet-beholdere.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Separator> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: - You explicitly create the item containers to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.
trans-unit.target: -Du Opprett eksplisitt beholderne som elementet til <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: For more information about explicitly versus implicitly creating item containers, see the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om eksplisitt sammenlignet opprette implisitt elementet beholdere, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>klasse.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: When a VirtualizingPanel is virtualizing item containers, you may need to save state information that is associated with a container instead of with the data item itself.
trans-unit.target: Når en VirtualizingPanel virtualisering elementet beholdere, må du kanskje lagre statusinformasjon som er knyttet til en beholder i stedet for med dataelementet seg selv.

trans-unit.source: For example, if an item is contained by an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander> control, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A> state is bound to the item container, and not to the data item itself.
trans-unit.target: Hvis som inneholder et element for eksempel en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander>kontroll av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A>tilstand er bundet til elementbeholderen, og ikke dataelementet seg selv.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander> is reused for a new item, the current value of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A> is used for the new item.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander>brukes på nytt for et nytt element, gjeldende verdi for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A>brukes for det nye elementet.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander>

trans-unit.source: In addition, the old item does not retain its <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A> value.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg gamle elementet beholder ikke den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A>verdi.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Expander.IsExpanded%2A>
